title: World of Warcraft WOTLK 3.3.5a Setup for Fight or Flight Gaming
description:
World of Warcraft WOTLK 3.3.5a preconfigured to run off the fight or flight gaming servers.  If you have a different private server you would like to connect to you will need to edit the realmlist.wtf file in the wow directory.

If you want to play on the fight or flight gaming server you need to download this torrent and create a account at www.fightorflightgaming.com/arcemu

You then just launch wow.exe and type in the account name and password you created there.

This is the fully installed game.
